How liberal democracy might lose the 21st centuryA scary little theory about information and freedom. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-liberal-democracy-might-lose https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-liberal-democracy-might-loseNoah Smith Wed, 22 May 2024 21:49:31 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg" width="1200" height="578" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:578,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:83339,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>我是在一个自由必胜主义的时代长大的。自由民主赢得了20世纪——帝国主义、法西斯主义和共产主义全部崩溃，到本世纪末，美国及其在亚洲和欧洲的民主盟友在经济和军事上都取得了优势。即使是仍然是专制国家的中国，也在这段时间内实现了经济和部分社会的自由化。即使是对弗朗西斯·福山的“历史终结”嗤之以鼻的学者也普遍支持资本主义和/或自由民主促进<a href="https://pages.ucsd.edu/~egartzke/publications/gartzke_ajps_07.pdf">和平</a>、<a href="https://www.bu.edu/sthacker/files/2012/01/Democracy-and-Human-Development.pdf">幸福</a>和<a href="https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1540-5907.2007.00299.x">繁荣</a>的论点。人们有一种压倒性的感觉，那就是自由——表达你的想法的自由，按照你喜欢的方式生活，购买和出售你想要的东西的自由——才是<em>胜利的关键</em>。</p><p>仅仅二十年后，这个想法就受到了严重质疑。民主化和社会自由化的浪潮<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-darkness">出现逆转</a>。美国社会和政治混乱四分五裂，制造业和住宅建设的弱点暴露无遗。与此同时，在习近平的领导下，21世纪初<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/china-at-the-peak">崛起的超级大国</a>中国又<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-governing-china-after-the-boom/?sref=R8NfLgwS">回到了</a>更加独裁的经济和更加极权的社会。</p><p>我认识的一些最近去中国旅行的人回来后都对中国与美国相比有多么美好的幻想： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg" width="656" height="839" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot